1. *Zabrinut* sam za budućnost svoje zemlje. (I am *concerned* about the future of my country.)
2. Naša mama je *zabrinuta* zbog nas. (Our mom is *worried* about us.)
3. Oni su veoma *zabrinuti* za sigurnost svoje kuće. (They are very *anxious* about the security of their house.)
4. Nadležne institucije su *zabrinute* zbog povećanja broja zaraženih. (The relevant institutions are *concerned* about the increase in the number of infected people.)
5. Kada je došla kući, primetila je da joj se pas čudno ponaša i bila je *zabrinuta*. (When she came home, she noticed that her dog was behaving strangely and she was *worried*.)
6. Doktori su bili *zabrinuti* za njegovo zdravlje, ali na kraju je sve ispalo u redu. (The doctors were *concerned* about his health, but in the end everything turned out okay.)
7. *Zabrinuto* je gledao u nebo koje se sve više oblačilo. (*Worriedly*, he watched the sky that was getting cloudier and cloudier.)
8. Iako je bio *zabrinut*, nije želeo da pokaže strah pred drugima. (Although he was *concerned*, he didn't want to show fear in front of others.)
9. Njihova mama je uvek *zabrinuta* kada se kasno vrate kući. (Their mom is always *worried* when they come home late.)
10. Svi smo bili *zabrinuti* zbog oluje koja je najavljena za večeras. (We were all *anxious* about the storm that was announced for tonight.)